---------------------------------------------
Handaxe with Slasher Feat - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Handaxe-Slasher-Str-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Disadvantage3-Nested}} 
---------------------------------------------
Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee/Ranged Attack - Handaxe&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Handaxe attack at a target within range (Melee/20'/60')*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d6!cf<1cs>6 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Slashing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Slashing + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals slashing damage, you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125; {{Slasher Crit=When you score a critical hit that deals slashing damage to a creature, you grievously wound it. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls.&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
Handaxe-Slasher-Str-Advantage-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee/Ranged Attack - Handaxe (Advantage)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Handaxe attack at a target within range (Melee/20'/60') at **Advantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[2d6!!cf<1cs>6kh1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Slashing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Slashing + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals slashing damage, you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125; {{Slasher Crit=When you score a critical hit that deals slashing damage to a creature, you grievously wound it. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls.&#125;&#125;
