---------------------------------------------
Handaxe with Slasher Feat using Offhand- Unnested Macros - Works on it's own, but not in a nested query
---------------------------------------------
Handaxe-Slasher-Str-OffHand--Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Melee/Ranged Attack - Handaxe}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Handaxe attack at a target within range (Melee/20'/60')*}} [[ [[ [[1d6!cf<1cs>6 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Slashing}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[5]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[6]] **Total Damage** }} {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals slashing damage, you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.}} {{Slasher Crit=When you score a critical hit that deals slashing damage to a creature, you grievously wound it. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls.}}
---------------------------------------------
Handaxe-Slasher-Str-OffHand--Advantage
&{template:default} {{name=Melee/Ranged Attack - Handaxe (Advantage)}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Handaxe attack at a target within range (Melee/20'/60') at **Advantage** *}} [[ [[ [[2d6!!cf<1cs>6kh1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Slashing}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[5]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[6]] **Total Damage** }} {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals slashing damage, you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.}} {{Slasher Crit=When you score a critical hit that deals slashing damage to a creature, you grievously wound it. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls.}}
